  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In Post-Herpetic Neuralgia(PHN) patients:

        -  To conduct an explorative investigation of the efficacy and safety of repeated oral
           doses of TRK-700 via a randomized double blind comparative study

        -  To measure the plasma concentration of TRK-700 and its metabolites
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
